%N A395925 Number of rectangular plane partitions of n with exactly 3 rows.
%F A395925 G.f.: Sum_{k>=1} q^(3*k) * Product_{i=1..3} Product_{j=1..k} 1/(1 - q^(i+j-1)).
%e A395925 The a(5) = 2 matrices:
%e A395925   [3] [2]
%e A395925   [1] [2]
